{
  "stem": "16887.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When we walked, I can't remember how far-- several kilometers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we came to the woods.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we stayed in the woods all night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told us that-- to take a train that goes to Bialystok, which was, before the war, belonged to Poland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But during the war, Russia-- Russia occupied it because they made a pact.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans came that far, and the Russian [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's when they made the-- the strip of No Man's Land.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we-- was a little light, we start walking towards the railroad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we came there, we waited I can't remember how long until the train came.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But by the time the train came, there was thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody's scared to get in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And somebody, again, shoved me in through the window.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't even know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were standing in the train like sardines.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "None of us knew if the other one got in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't remember how long it took until we came to be Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When we came to Bialystok and the train stopped, and everybody got out, that's when we met.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's when I saw my husband, and I saw my friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Luckily, everybody got in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were marching towards the city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We came into the city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All we had-- all I had was a little-- a few things on my back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the one pair of shoes, that's all we had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we came to Bialystok, the people were not too friendly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They called us [NON-ENGLISH], you know, like refugee.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They sort of were afraid of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [COUGHS] so we start asking where there's a concentration of the refugees where we could go.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And somebody pointed out to the outskirts of Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
